Resource Profile: Lab Observation: Microbiology Bacteriology Observation

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/LabObservationMicrobiologyBacteriologyObservation Version: 1.5.30
Draft as of 2025-05-25 Computable Name: LabObservationMicrobiologyBacteriologyObservation

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file MICROBIOLOGY (63.05) to us-core-observation-lab.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Lab Observation: Microbiology Bacteriology DiagnosticReport
  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: Lighthouse Clinical Health API and Lighthouse Patient Health API
